rComments: So nice and hilarious. The textbook was expensive, but everything we're reading for the course is in the anthology. Very fair and flexible, 10% is mark was participation, but instead of speaking in class, you could email her your participation for the week. I have heard of more interesting books being read in other sections, we are reading hp #1

Excellent prof.  Thorough explanations and expectations.  She has a playful personality and has a genuine interest in you succeeding.  Always well prepared and is very approachable for help.  I highly recommend her for this course.  Good luck.
